  "body": "I've been monitoring `eth_blockNumber` and I've noticed that it was updated before the blocks pass the full cycle of staged sync.\r\n\r\nIt actually uses the progress of execution phase, before state root is calculated and checked. That might lead to potentially malicious blocks being received via our RPC API with no checks.",
